  "body": " Properties of Equivalent Equations  Addition property of equality  Equation(s) addition property of equality for solving  Subtraction property of equality  Multiplication property of equality  Equation(s) multiplication property of equality for solving  Division property of equality   If there is an equation , we can do the following to obtain an equivalent equation.     (add the same number to each side)   (subtract the same number from each side)     (multiply each side of the equation by the same nonzero number)   (divide each side of the equation by the same nonzero number)     "
